wb-homa-drivers (1.8.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * w1 improvements: delete old entries from MQTT on startup,
   limit update rate
  * Add mqtt-logger utility
  * ADC subsystem: support for non-multiplexed channels,
   resistance measurement (not tested yet), report measurements in volts
  * GPIO driver:
       * interrupt support
       * pulse meter support (water and power meters)

  * Modbus-RTU driver:
      * Support for device templates

 -- Evgeny Boger <boger@contactless.ru>  Sun, 15 Mar 2015 16:12:26 +0300

